# Environment Configuration

## Development

```env
# API
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:3001/api

# Authentication
NEXTAUTH_URL=http://localhost:3000
NEXTAUTH_SECRET=your-secret-key-here

# Database
MONGODB_URI=mongodb://localhost:27017/artvince

# Image Optimization
NEXT_PUBLIC_IMAGE_CDN=

# Feature Flags
NEXT_PUBLIC_ENABLE_AUTH=true
NEXT_PUBLIC_ENABLE_ANALYTICS=false
```

## Production

```env
# API
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://api.artvince.com/api

# Authentication
NEXTAUTH_URL=https://artvince.com
NEXTAUTH_SECRET=your-production-secret

# Database
MONGODB_URI=mongodb+srv://user:pass@cluster.mongodb.net/artvince

# Image Optimization
NEXT_PUBLIC_IMAGE_CDN=https://cdn.artvince.com

# Feature Flags
NEXT_PUBLIC_ENABLE_AUTH=true
NEXT_PUBLIC_ENABLE_ANALYTICS=true
```

## Key Variables

- `NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL` - Backend API base URL
- `NEXTAUTH_URL` - Authentication callback URL
- `NEXTAUTH_SECRET` - Auth session secret (generate with `openssl rand -base64 32`)
- `MONGODB_URI` - Database connection string
- `NEXT_PUBLIC_IMAGE_CDN` - CDN for image optimization
